# Passed to `docker run --env-file .env` for local dev, and also how this
# database deploys on Bzync Cloud itself — this tier has no managed/linked
# database service (mdb was removed; see the workspace root `README.md`), so
# this template deployed as its own app *is* the database.
#
# MEILI_MASTER_KEY is deliberately not defaulted to the repo-standard
# "changeme" placeholder in the Dockerfile — Meilisearch requires at least
# 16 bytes in production mode and rejects anything shorter outright at
# startup (confirmed by testing). Generate a real one:
#   openssl rand -base64 24
MEILI_MASTER_KEY=
